title: Foster & Allen   -   2 Albums
description:
Foster and Allen are a musical duo from Ireland consisting of Mick Foster and Tony Allen. In their 40-year career they have released over 30 albums, many of which entered the UK Albums Chart. They started in the 1970s as a duo, but in 1982 (when the concert tours started) they added a band to their show. They have appeared on many television shows, including their own, and have achieved album and video sales in excess of 18 million worldwide.
